{"tid":2448321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"開車開冷氣唔行，再訓著係咪一定死到？","createTime":"2021-03-16T00:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T02:15:07.000Z","uid":77937,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"remark":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：\n[url]https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline[/url]","replies":[{"pid":"d0bd0c6de8a78fcd1a4c4e62c2ee6f2002563cb9","tid":2448321,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:06:01.000Z","msg":"想知"},{"pid":"8b135588737b4274aa2027a328c96dfb92b70bbe","tid":2448321,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:07:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16829dae389bd76a3dce0ff41fa63536965d43f3","tid":2448321,"uid":156936,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:07:36.000Z","msg":"您可獲得協助，立即找人傾訴<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線<br />\n<br />\n時間：24小時。語言：廣東話。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n瞭解詳情：2382 0000"},{"pid":"72b1059a5751667075963c1238eb47aa47ec8954","tid":2448321,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:08:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac48632b21c4458a751a2a5cdcdfa26f7ce82121","tid":2448321,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:09:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe3687ec4aa5eda38387f9a09811c17dd7b78adc","tid":2448321,"uid":89955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:11:27.000Z","msg":"請珍惜生命，謝謝"},{"pid":"1b8edff8c1286a8211815be56fb7c4f910537447","tid":2448321,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:20:15.000Z","msg":"唔會"},{"pid":"9219a5a38be788344a6d6e9493196cc64d6f2867","tid":2448321,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:36:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0fc1171a4f2feb55853559d514fada42f27467a","tid":2448321,"uid":17443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:37:29.000Z","msg":"換冷氣泵"},{"pid":"24d4f04bb3f70b4fbf4ee5caa3828c42af49dd85","tid":2448321,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:38:33.000Z","msg":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。<br />\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline</a>"},{"pid":"348bd342975f6235492e22e1e7a3ec15696ea7df","tid":2448321,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:38:36.000Z","msg":"算啦，其實要搵都會搵到答案，係睇幾時做，多謝大家"},{"pid":"8c7de307d0f79c10c34e978a33da982cef696723","tid":2448321,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:39:43.000Z","msg":"Plini，看來你心中盛載著的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀。人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，到我們的網站 <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=a6caf7dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（ <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=ea99b26e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a> ）。 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：下午4時至凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期：晚上８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"c79c00dc364aa855d1039142b56984eb42d22f29","tid":2448321,"uid":180379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:40:33.000Z","msg":"有咩問題 好多人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e29e4234db912913f8a57736133a3435e8a47f","tid":2448321,"uid":30972,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3